Package: MSMGOptimizer
Type: Package
Title: MSMG SimaPro CSV Optimizer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Philip", "Duah",
      email = "dpbxc@mst.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Transforms raw life cycle inventory (LCI) data into
    a fully compatible CSV format that can be imported seamlessly
    into SimaPro for life cycle assessment workflows. Developed as
    part of the project 'ECO-CBET: GOALI: CAS-Climate: Expediting
    Decarbonization of the Cement Industry through Integration of
    CO2 Capture and Conversion' (NSF Project No. 2219086).
URL: https://github.com/Duah-Philip/MSMGOptimizer
BugReports: https://github.com/Duah-Philip/MSMGOptimizer/issues
